FT  14 APR 94 / World News in Brief: Greece to seize ex-king's property
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The Greek parliament passed a bill to seize the property of ex-king
Constantine and strip his family of their Greek passports. Pasok rivals
jockey to succeed Papandreou, Page 3
</TEXT>
<XX>
