FT  13 APR 94 / The Lex Column: Laura Ashley
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Jim Maxmin has always looked vaguely ill at ease in Laura Ashley. So his
departure from the chief executive's slot is perhaps unsurprising. Some of
the company's operational problems have been sorted out in the last three
years. Others, most notably in the US, have not. Several of the more serious
